<lb n="0645b27" ed="T"/>囉<note n="0645b2701" resp="CBETA" type="add">鄔【CB】，鄥【大】</note><app n="0645b2701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">鄔</lem><rdg wit="【大】">鄥</rdg></app>那囉尾誐摩三摩鉢地簸他輸地鉢他奴
<lb n="0645b28" ed="T"/>誐摩鉢他輸地鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>枳娘<note place="inline">二合</note>目谿阿哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>
